title: [Greymist Wood]
description: Soft shafts of moonlight create a striking pattern, which knifes through the jungle darkness on all sides.  The trail curves around the monstrous bole of a yintosh tree, its thick buttress root system offering a veritable maze of shadowed crevices and cubbyholes.  A carpet of the yintosh's broad leaves lie around the tree's perimeter, their curled edges cradling puddles of water where the moonbeams are reflected here and there.

Stark shafts of light create a striking pattern, which knifes through the jungle murk tinged a mossy green by the thick foliage on all sides.  The trail curves around the monstrous bole of a yintosh tree, its thick buttress root system offering a veritable maze of hiding crevices and cubbyholes.  A carpet of the yintosh's broad leaves lie around the tree's perimeter, their curled edges cradling puddles of water where tadpoles and mosquito larva dwell.
